; The fennec.pulse.collection ppx RULES as a plain library — NOT a ppx_rewriter. The reusable core
; (the [@@deriving fennec_collection] deriver + the [%fields] projection extension); both fur.ppx
; and the standalone fennec.pulse.collection.ppx link it and register the same rules in their own
; driver, so a file pays ONE ppx process regardless of which it uses.
(library
 (name fennec_pulse_collection_ppx_rules)
 (public_name fennec.pulse.collection.ppx.rules)
 (libraries ppxlib)
 (preprocess (pps ppxlib.metaquot)))
